{
  "id": "6a057aa83b64c8d5e9e7e164",
  "title": "coscli",
  "created": 1778743976,
  "updated": 1778750708,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a057aa83b64c8d5e9e7e164",
      "text": "coscli",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057e4d0000000000efc791",
      "text": "https://github.com/mtane0412/coscli",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744910,
      "updated": 1778744910
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057e4e0000000000efc792",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744910,
      "updated": 1778744910
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000505570",
      "text": "coscli は [[Cosense]] (旧 Scrapbox) 向けの AI エージェント親和的 CLI ツール。バイナリ名は `cos`。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000d63f6b",
      "text": "ターミナル・スクリプト・CI・AIエージェントから Cosense のページを操作できる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000c29fa4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000008f111e",
      "text": "[*** Cosenseユーザーとして嬉しいこと]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000008d9afe",
      "text": "[** ページをターミナルから操作できる]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000002c6b72",
      "text": "`cos page list --project myproject` でページ一覧を取得",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000a56f5d",
      "text": "`cos page new` でページを作成、`cos page append` で末尾に追記",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000c01717",
      "text": "`cos page watch` でページ更新をリアルタイム監視（tail -f 感覚）",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000004fe709",
      "text": "ブラウザを開かずにページの操作が一通りできるのが地味に便利。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000c75d72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000522914",
      "text": "[** Markdown ↔ Scrapbox 記法を相互変換できる]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000009b5cee",
      "text": "`cos convert --from=md --to=scrapbox --from-file input.md`",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000cd1a87",
      "text": "書き慣れたMarkdownをそのままCosenseに持ち込める。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000044a37d",
      "text": "逆にCosenseの内容をMarkdownに書き出すことも。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000fc9eae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000ac22bd",
      "text": "[** ローカルファイルと同期できる]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000d48b53",
      "text": "`cos sync pull --all --dir ./pages` で全ページをローカルに落とす",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000009b7c66",
      "text": "`cos sync push` でローカルの変更をアップロード",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000001b2801",
      "text": "お気に入りのテキストエディタでCosenseを編集したい人に刺さる機能。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000044b3d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000002b11db",
      "text": "[*** AIエージェントとして嬉しいこと]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000009a842d",
      "text": "[** Cosenseをナレッジベースとして活用できる]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000007cf747",
      "text": "coscliを使うと、Cosenseに蓄積した知識をエージェントが直接読み書きできる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000008807f2",
      "text": "「調べる → Cosenseで確認 → 結果を記録」というループをエージェントが自律的に回せる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000a3b7cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000006d1408",
      "text": "[** Smart Context でリンク先の文脈を一括取得できる]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000ff6df4",
      "text": "`cos page context \"起点ページ\" --project myproject`",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000b116fa",
      "text": "Cosenseのページはリンクで有機的につながっている。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000004e7ff0",
      "text": "page context はリンク先ページの本文テキストをまとめて返してくれるので、関連する文脈を一括でLLMに渡せる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000004b1c43",
      "text": "「このページと周辺知識」をセットで入手できるのはエージェントにとって強力。RAGっぽく使える。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000b83ce4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000063169b",
      "text": "[** JSON出力 + セレクタでトークンを節約できる]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000c0285d",
      "text": "`cos page list --json --results-only --select 'pages[].title'`",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000003a5e63",
      "text": "--json --results-only --select の組み合わせで必要なデータだけをミニマルに取得。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000bd1c25",
      "text": "エージェントが不要なデータに惑わされず、トークン消費も最小限に抑えられる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000ac6602",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000001b7dde",
      "text": "[** Sandboxでコマンドを安全に制限できる]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000c81c13",
      "text": "`cos --enable-commands \"page.list,page.get,page.text,search\" page list`",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000002f1862",
      "text": "どのコマンドを使っていいかを明示的に制御できる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000fd5e56",
      "text": "読み取り専用に制限したエージェントを作るのが簡単。違反時は exit 7 で明確に検知できる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0582e700000000004076df",
      "text": "　ここの引数自体をエージェントが書き換えるというのはできないようにできるんですか?[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778746087,
      "updated": 1778746098
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000008f42b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000ffb8eb",
      "text": "[** 機械可読な終了コードでエラーハンドリングが明確]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000009f4679",
      "text": "`cos exit-codes --json` で全種類の終了コードを取得",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000f14b76",
      "text": "exit 2 なら再認証、exit 4 なら新規作成、exit 6 なら pull してリトライ、と状態に応じた自動回復が書きやすい。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000ac85f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000aa093d",
      "text": "[** --dry-run で安全に確認してから実行]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000139a84",
      "text": "`cos page edit \"タイトル\" --from-file content.md --dry-run`",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000026f6d5",
      "text": "書き込み系コマンドはすべて --dry-run に対応。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000038b712",
      "text": "エージェントが本番を間違って変更する事故を防げる。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000002617dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000000c6c69",
      "text": "[*** 主なコマンド]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000003d4c4b",
      "text": "table:コマンド一覧",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000f4644d",
      "text": "\tコマンド\t概要",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000008fa1c2",
      "text": "\tcos page list\tページ一覧取得",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000313969",
      "text": "\tcos page get\tページ詳細取得",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000060850",
      "text": "\tcos page text\tページ本文テキスト取得",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000da4397",
      "text": "\tcos page context\tリンク先ページの文脈を一括取得（Smart Context）",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000094a633",
      "text": "\tcos page new\tページ新規作成",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000054d005",
      "text": "\tcos page edit\tページ全置換",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000003b0619",
      "text": "\tcos page append\tページ末尾に追記",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd300000087a9a6",
      "text": "\tcos page watch\tページ更新をリアルタイム監視",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000005381ae",
      "text": "\tcos search\tページ検索",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000002851a9",
      "text": "\tcos sync pull / cos sync push\tローカルファイルとの同期",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000275572",
      "text": "\tcos convert\tScrapbox記法 ↔ Markdown 変換",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057be255cbd3000000c97475",
      "text": "\tcos serve --rest\tローカルRESTプロキシサーバー起動",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744291,
      "updated": 1778744291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000db6496",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000007b2634",
      "text": "[*** インストール]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000aa1fd6",
      "text": "`brew tap mtane0412/coscli`",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000fd761c",
      "text": "`brew install coscli`",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778744710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000617f52",
      "text": "詳細は [https://github.com/mtane0412/coscli GitHub] を参照。",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd30000007c141f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057aa855cbd3000000acefd3",
      "text": "#cli #cosense #aiagent",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778743976,
      "updated": 1778743976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057dc10000000000efc783",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744769,
      "updated": 1778744769
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057dc10000000000efc784",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744769,
      "updated": 1778744771
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057dcd0000000000efc789",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744781,
      "updated": 1778744781
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057dc10000000000efc785",
      "text": "coscli使ってclaude codeに書かせた[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744770,
      "updated": 1778744781
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057dcb0000000000efc787",
      "text": " https://github.com/mtane0412/coscli",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744780,
      "updated": 1778744780
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057dcb0000000000efc788",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/662661d0f9b1fd1d4fdb4460b31de611]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778744780,
      "updated": 1778744780
    },
    {
      "id": "6a057dce0000000000efc78a",
